Allianz App Privacy Policy & Terms of Use
Acknowledgement
Thank you for choosing this mobile phone application (“Application”). This Application enables the user access to relevant information, roadside assistance services in emergency situations, relevant resources, claims submission services and tools, request for Guarantee Letters and updates on respective company products (“Insurance Services”) from Allianz General Insurance Company (Malaysia) Berhad (“AGIC”) or Allianz Life Insurance Malaysia Berhad (“ALIM”). (AGIC and ALIM shall collectively be referred to as “Allianz Malaysia”). The terms “we,” “our,” and “us” in these Terms refer to Allianz Malaysia.
Privacy Policy
We value your trust. In turn, we guard that trust by respecting your privacy, particularly as it relates to maintaining the confidentiality or any personal data received. This notice explains the types of personal data collected through this Application, how it is used and the circumstances under which it may be disclosed. This Privacy Policy is for the use of this Application. This Policy applies only to the data received in connection with your use of this Application and does not apply to data received from third parties or to information that is publicly available. We may amend this Privacy Policy in line with the relevant law and internal group policies from time to time and the latest Policy shall take precedence over any previous Privacy Policies issued related to this Application.
Choice & Consent
Personal data is captured when using this Application to help us provide useful assistance and support for the Allianz User and/or Non-Allianz User. When you use this Application, the personal profile is voluntarily furnished by you, whether as an Allianz User or otherwise. We limit the information we collect from you while using this Application to what is necessary to administer our business, provide superior service, offer opportunities that we think would be of benefit to you whether as an Allianz User or otherwise and ensure technological compatibility with your Device. You may choose whether or not to provide your personal data to us. If you choose not to do so, we may not be able to provide you with the services you requested. If you provide your personal data including any sensitive personal data such as health or medical conditions and use the Application, you are deemed to have granted your consent for us to collect, process, maintain, transmit, use and store your personal data including the sensitive personal data for the purposes stated in this notice. You may choose to revoke your consent by notifying us in writing and thereafter cease to use by uninstalling this Application.
Automatically Collected Information
Every time you view or use this Application some information is automatically collected about you. This information may include, but is not limited to, some or all the following items: the specific pages, buttons, images, videos, links, or forms that you access on this Application; the type and version of software and operating system you use; date, time, and duration of your use; your IP address; type of Device (e.g. laptop, iPad, Blackberry, iPhone); mobile carrier and/or internet service provider; the location of your Device, and demographic information concerning the country of origin of your Device and the languages it uses.
How we use and disclose your information
Most of the information we collect is used to help deliver the Insurance Services available from this Application as requested. It also may permit us to design and offer specific products and services that will be useful to our customers, or that provide benefits, additional value or discounts. From time to time, we may use and share information that personally identifies you to our third party service providers, our affiliates and to other non-affiliated entities including in the following manner:
In response to judicial proceeding, subpoena, court order or other legal process;
To comply with legal, regulatory or administrative requirements of governmental authorities;
To protect the rights or property of Allianz Malaysia including clients, suppliers or customers, and to enforce the provisions of terms or policies, in cases of customer fraud or disputes, and/or to prevent harm to you or others;
As disclosed in other applicable policies, terms of use, or other agreements;
To manage and service you and provide you with better customer service including marketing and promoting other products and services by Allianz Malaysia, its appointed third party service providers and its group of companies and their affiliates; or
As permitted or required by law or as authorized by you.
You agree that we and our affiliates may collect and use technical and related information, including but not limited to information about your Device, system, application software, peripherals, and other similar information, that is gathered periodically to facilitate the provision of software updates, product support and other services to you (if any) related to this Application, and to verify compliance with these Terms. We may also use this information to improve our products or to provide better services or technologies to you moving forward.
Some services provided through this Application may rely upon location information. To provide these services Allianz Malaysia, its affiliates, its appointed third party service providers and partners may transmit, collect, maintain process and use your location data, including the real-time geographic location of your Device. By using this Application, you agree and consent to Allianz Malaysia its appointed service providers and partners’ transmission, collection, maintenance, processing and use of your location data to provide you with the requested services. The location data is collected in a form that personally identifies you and/or your vehicles.
Our definition of personally identifiable information does not include “aggregate” information. Aggregate information is data we collect about a group or category of products, services or customers, from which individual customer identities have been removed. In other words, information about how you use a service may be collected and combined with information about how others use the same service, but no personally identifiable information will be included in the resulting data. Likewise, information about the products you purchased may be collected and combined with information about products purchased by others. Aggregate data helps us understand trends and customer needs so that we can better consider new products and services, and tailor existing products and services desired by customers.
Your Rights of Access to Your Personal Data
You have the right to access and make corrections to your personal data processed by us with a request in writing via email and you may make any enquiries or complaints in respect of your personal data by contacting Allianz’s Customer Service Officer at 1300-22-5542, from 9.00 a.m. to 6.00 p.m., Monday to Friday or email at
customer.service@allianz.com.my
or via our Fax No. 03-2264 8499.
You also have the right to request in writing for Allianz Malaysia to cease processing your personal data including for marketing purposes.
Security
We maintain security standards that are designed to help us protect your information. While we use such security standards, we cannot guarantee that personally identifiable information you submit on this Application, whilst involving and interacting with third party hardware, software, services and applications, will be secure or that such third party services will be secure or will be uninterrupted or error-free.
Links and External Websites
This Application may contain links to and from websites. We make no representations whatsoever about any other website that you may have accessed from our website or through this Application. We are not responsible for the privacy practices or content of those websites and we expressly deny any liability whatsoever for use of such websites.
Notice to Persons Accessing this Application Outside Malaysia
If you reside outside Malaysia, any information you provide to us on this Application will be transferred out of your country and into Malaysia. If you do not want your personally identifiable information to leave your country, please do not provide the information to us. By providing personally identifiable information to us, you explicitly consent to the transfer of your information to Malaysia. Personally identifiable information collected on this Application or during the provision of Services may be stored and processed in Malaysia or any other country in which we or our affiliates, subsidiaries or service providers maintain facilities.
Use of this Application by Children
We do no intend to collect information from children who are under 18 years of age. If you are under 18, you should not provide information in this Application without your parents’ or legal guardian’s consent.
