This End User Agreement and its terms including the Privacy Policy for the Application (“Terms”) is between the user and Allianz Malaysia on the use of this Application and all related updates and upgrades that replace or supplement this Application (“License”).
Allianz User
As a customer of AGIC and/or ALIM (“Allianz User”) you are eligible to receive the relevant Insurance Services from AGIC or ALIM respectively as described under the terms and conditions of your insurance cover with AGIC or ALIM when you use this Application. Please refer to the insurance policy documents you received from Allianz Malaysia as a customer for the terms and conditions of the relevant Insurance Services.
As an Allianz User you may establish an account in this Application (“Account”). You are solely responsible for maintaining the confidentiality and security of your Account and for all activities that occur on or through your Account. Therefore, do not reveal your Account information to anyone else. You agree to immediately notify Allianz Malaysia of any security breach of your Account.
Non-Allianz User
If you are not an Allianz User or if you are no longer covered under any of Allianz Malaysia’s insurance coverage you can still use this Application to obtain emergency contacts, panel listings, marketing information and other information that is published in this Application.
